{"tid":1093510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[當年今日】1975年4月5日 蔣介石逝世","createTime":"2019-04-05T15:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T05:58:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f74b6ef5f94de8d621c326c9ddd3445bf1e5f7dd","tid":1093510,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"今日除咗係清明節，亦都係國民政府前總統蔣介石嘅死忌。1975年4月5日，蔣介石喺士林官邸心臟病發逝世，終年87歲。佢嘅太太宋美齡、蔣經國按照蔣介石嘅遺願，將靈柩安放喺慈湖陵寢。蔣介石一生傳奇，做過黃埔軍校校長，帶領國民黨推翻北洋政府，並參與抗日同國共內戰。<br />\n<br />\n其中，「西安事變」可以話改變咗中國嘅發展，以及蔣介石嘅一生。1936年國民政府東北軍主帥張學良同西北軍主帥楊虎城發動兵諫，脅逼蔣介石停止剿共，合作抗日。最後喺南京政府「和平救蔣」策略之下，經過多番斡旋同談判，蔣介石承諾停止剿共、聯合抗日，張學良親自陪蔣介石返南京，其後被軟禁至1990年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://shifiles.looop.hk/posts/7972/%E8%94%A3%E4%BB%8B%E7%9F%B3%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96?fbclid=IwAR23zb1nRlpc5J3eOj1F1MGjWybwdE51xPfgWUHld7gVyP1Wpv84oJCOK3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshifiles.looop.hk%2Fposts%2F7972%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR23zb1nRlpc5J3eOj1F1MGjWybwdE51xPfgWUHld7gVyP1Wpv84oJCOK3s&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=adb47a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shifiles.looop.hk/posts/7972/%E8%94%A3%E4%BB%8B%E7%9F%B3%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96?fbclid=IwAR23zb1nRlpc5J3eOj1F1MGjWybwdE51xPfgWUHld7gVyP1Wpv84oJCOK3s</a>"},{"pid":"b071f155e53fd5bc540eac76e0528a4261ebc267","tid":1093510,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"none care"},{"pid":"cd4f321c44c11fecf982efe501573d0a9c0f261f","tid":1093510,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"張學良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71b0780c6223c28350c3625e8ffd2d3fdf092eb","tid":1093510,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"係中華民國政府"},{"pid":"c26433a91e88ec5f20118fb37f7d90c12cc1071b","tid":1093510,"uid":2471